data.text:
Zoe Salmon is a television presenter from Northern Ireland. She hosted the children's television programme Blue Peter from 23 December 2004 to 25 June 2008. In 1999, was crowned Miss Northern Ireland.

Zoe was a contestant in Series 4, partnering American pair skater Matt Evers and finished in 5th place after loosing to Jessica Taylor in the save me skate. She was the ninth celebrity eliminated in week nine in a 4:1 judges' vote, with only Ruthie Henshall choosing to save her. Zoe had appeared in the bottom two the previous week eliminating Emmerdale actress Roxanne Pallett.
